Operation Pizzasplat
{{potential}}

When [[i|insurgents]] get bored, there's always trouble afoot. As was the case on the day in question. A target was chosen; a paintball store in [[Texas]] with a [[camwhore|webcam]]. The harpoons were fired, starting with a wave of prank calls.

=First shots fired=
[[Image:33278132.jpg|thumb|400px|right|Before and After the attacks.]]
The harpoons were fired, with nigra's leading the way with an infantry attack of phone calls.
His smiling demeanor turned quickly downhill as his [[fat|character]] was attacked for refusing to sell his [[jewgold|horde]] of [[Battletoads]].

{{quote|''I DONT HAVE FUCKING BATTLETOADS FUCKER''|fatty}}

==The Plan==
Since Cableguy found the whole site, three users (The_cow, The CableGuy, And JollyNigra) watched the place for awhile. After awhile, JollyNigra formed a plan to order [[pizza|pizza]] for the whole shop. After a couple of calls asking about battletoads and shit, Many people started asking for the pizza order when a bunch of customers came in asking for a [[rape|match]]. Eventually they put a towel over the cam.

==The Order info==
The order, from Pizza Hut, was simple...

*1 PANormous with meat stuff
*XTRA Everything except toppings
*2x 2-liter Moutain Dews
*A note saying, "I ordered this for you"
*40 Burning hot wings
*cinnamon [[dick|sticks]] with double [[cum|icing]].

{{quote|"58 FUCKING BUCKS!"|JollyNigra}}

