=The Second Strike=
The store nextdoor was the next to be hit, with autodials and insults coming. As with the first, pizza was ordered. Unfortunately, the store was [[fail|closed]] by the time it should have been delivered.

===Second Order===
From Dominoes pizza:

*16" Brooklyn pizza, xtra cheese, all the meat toppings
*1 8 piece breadsticks
*1 three chese mac-n-cheese pasta
*2 8 piece cinna-stix.

Grand total of $32.37

